V//"It may not be Jakuta, but it's still a habitable planet. Initial scans show promise, so be diligent and the colony will thrive. The Heroism exhausted its FTL to bring us here. Let's not squander the opportunity that luck has brought us."//  Captain Scott's message to the crew was clear: this is our new home.\u000a\u000a//"The rest of the crew will awaken in a few months, so let's have a functional colony waiting for them. I will remain aboard the Heroism to keep her systems online until then. I expect you all to perform your duties with utmost efficiency. Remember, this is the moment you've all trained for. Good luck."// All around you, various crew are gathering supplies and equipping protective gear.\u000a\u000a[[Suit up.|StartSlow2]]
