VYou focus on equipping all of your protective gear. Forgetting any small detail now could get you killed planetside. You finish your ensemble with a belt of handy tools and an oxygen tank, just in case.\u000a\u000aYou notice your friend Soto at the other end of the room, already fully geared and heading toward the drop pods. You consider catching up with him to chat, but he's moving at a fast pace. Oh well, you'll have a chance to catch up with him at the colony's power plant.\u000a\u000a[[Best get a move to the drop pods.|Start4]]
