V<<if visited() is 1>>Stepping out of the pod, you are nearly overwhelmed by the sights of the colony and the landscape. Twin suns shine brilliantly in the crisp blue sky overhead. Tall mountains line the horizon to the north, and all around you are clean prefabricated structures. To the east is a very distinct building, the power plant of the colony, where you expect to find your technician friend Soto.\u000a\u000a[[Head east to the power plant.|Power Plant]]\u000a\u000aFrom the south approach a trio of robots, likely here to retrieve the pod. The ships roboticist Terra is probably manging them right now from the robotics lab. Anything menial has to be handled by the robots, since there's only seven people managing this entire colony right now. You will probably need to stop by sooner rather than later..\u000a\u000a[[Head south to the robotics lab.|Robotics Lab]]\u000a\u000aYou hear a belching noise come from the north, and a plume of smoke erupts from the closest prefab to the north. You surmise it to be the colony's manufacturing. Lucy's probably trying to get a head start on the industrial needs of the colony. She's hard to get along with, but if you need anything fabricated she's the only one who can do it.\u000a\u000a[[Head north to the factory.|Factory]]\u000a\u000aYour radio sounds out a familiar voice. //"Pleasant landing, I hope? This is Lya, come see me at the colony center. It's the big dome-shaped building west of where you landed." // You recognize administrator Lya's voice, and judging by her tone she's probably got your task in mind already.\u000a\u000a[[Head west to the colony center.|Colony Center]]\u000a\u000a<<else>>This is the direct center of the colony, a flat clearing ideal for receiving pods and shipments from the Heroism. There's a few piles of supplies lying around and paths to every other part of the colony. The skies are clear. Nothing will arrive anytime soon.\u000a\u000a<<if $comm_array > 1 and $refinery > 1 and $spaceport is 0>>There's a pile of alloys here and an unattached link to the colony center. This would be an ideal location to build the spaceport to get back to the Heroism.\u000a\u000a[[//"Terra, have the bots start assembling the spaceport."//|Build Spaceport]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $spaceport is 1>>Robots are hard at work in this area, laying out sheets of alloy and fusing them together. The incomplete launch tower grows taller by the minute. The colony should be ready to launch in no time.\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $spaceport is 2>>The colony's spaceport is here, a flat metal base with a launch tower, ready to launch cargo and people up to the Heroism. Dwayne sits inside, keeping track of the Heroism's location.\u000a\u000a[[Enter the spaceport.|Spaceport]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>>[[Head north to the factory.|Factory]]\u000a\u000a[[Head south to the robotics lab.|Robotics Lab]]\u000a\u000a[[Head east to the power plant.|Power Plant]]\u000a\u000a[[Head west to the colony center.|Colony Center]]\u000a\u000a\u000a<<endif>>
