V<<if visited() is 1>>You approach the factory, a set of industrial appliances which are designed to collectively fabricate anything and everything that the colony needs. Lucy, the colony's engineer and caretaker of this equipment, stands with arms folded in front of a running 3D printer. She doesn't appear to notice you.\u000a\u000a<<else>>You stand outside of the factory, a cluster of industrial equipment which produces everything for the colony. Lucy is standing here, <<if $flight_suit is 1>>piecing together parts of an outfit with thin metal wings.<<elseif $boat is 1>>watching a 3D printer fabricate the hull of a boat.<<elseif $stasis_net is 1>>working a thin harness through a lithomagnet.<<elseif $bomb is 1>>monitoring a centrifuge as it spins at dizzying speeds.<<else>>assembling a robot for farming work.<<endif>>\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $refinery is 1>>Robots are hard at work in this area, building silos and connecting pipes. The smelter they're working on should be ideal for processing the complex ores and fuels found on the planet.\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $refinery is 2>>Off to the side is the industrial smelter. It flows with molten metal, extracting waste material and processing the metal into usable alloys.\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $need_flight_suit and $flight_suit is 0>>Lucy should be able to help you with your elevation problem.\u000a\u000a[[//"Lucy, I need a flight suit."//|Flight Suit]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $need_boat and $boat is 0>>Making a portable boat to get to that island should be no problem for Lucy.\u000a\u000a[[//"Lucy, I need a boat."//|Boat]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if visited("Island") and $refinery and $bomb is 0>>If anyone can blow up that tower, Lucy can.\u000a\u000a[[//"Lucy, I need a bomb. Something to topple a tower."//|Bomb]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if visited("Bio Lab") and visited("Beast Den") and $stasis_net is 0>>Capturing a wild animal will be no easy task. Lucy should be able to build something to help you out. \u000a\u000a[[//"Lucy, I need something to capture a live animal."//|Build Stasis Net]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if visited("Cave") and $refinery is 0>>The rare ores on this planet take a lot of energy to be processed into tougher alloys. Having the robots build a smelter here will solve that.\u000a\u000a[[//"Terra, send the robots to build a smelter at the factory, please. Ask Lucy for the specs."//|Build Refinery]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if visited() is 1>>The path north leads out of the colony, toward the mountains.\u000a\u000a<<endif>>[[Leave the colony, heading north toward the mountains.|North of Colony]]\u000a\u000a<<if visited() is 1>>The path south leads back to the landing area and the center of the colony.\u000a\u000a<<endif>>[[Head south to the center of the colony.|Hub]]
