f>>[[Head north to the center of the colony.|Hub]]\u000a\u000a<<if visited() is 1>>The path south leads out of the colony, towards a clearing with a high view of the planet's murky blue ocean.\u000a\u000a<<endif>>[[Leave the colony, heading south toward the ocean.|South of Colony]]\u000a\u000a<<if $bio_lab > 1>><<if visited("Bio Lab") is 0>>The path east leads to the bio lab, a smooth rectangular building decorated with long windows and lab equipment. \u000a\u000a<<endif>>[[Head east to the bio lab.|Bio Lab]]\u000a\u000a<<endif>>
