VThe night passes quietly, and you awaken the next morning feeling <<if $doom_disease < 4>>sickly. Your body appears to be covered in small growths, likely the result of some native disease. It appears that the others are also afflicted.<<else>>rested<<endif>>.\u000a\u000a<<if $aux_gen is 1>><<set $aux_gen to 2>>Work on the solar farm has completed.\u000a\u000a<<elseif $aux_gen > 1>><<set $generator += 1>><<endif>><<if $fusion_gen is 1>><<set $fusion_gen to 2>>Work on the fusion reactor has completed.\u000a\u000a<<elseif $fusion_gen > 1>><<set $generator += 1>><<endif>><<if $fuel>><<set $fuel -= 1>><<set $generator += 1>><<endif>><<if $mountain_mapped is 1>>The robots have completed mapping the northern mountains. They found one spot that looks like it might contain some useful ores that would be worth digging out.\u000a\u000a<<set $mountain_mapped to 2>><<endif>><<if $forest_mapped is 1>>The robots have completed mapping the western forest. Among the general flora and fauna they found a strange fungal growth that could be worth investigating. Inez mentions that she could analyze what you bring back, but she'd need a biology lab built first.\u000a\u000a<<set $forest_mapped to 2>><<endif>><<if $hills_mapped is 1>>The robots have completed mapping the eastern hills. They located a den of beasts not too far in to the hills.\u000a\u000a<<set $hills_mapped to 2>><<endif>><<if $weather_tower is 1>>The robots have completed the weather tower. You hear a good forecast for weather this week, should be good to sail.\u000a\u000a<<set $weather_tower to 2>><<endif>><<if $comm_array is 1>>The robots have completed rebuilding the communications equipment. Lya is already having a conversation with Captain Scott this morning.\u000a\u000a<<set $comm_array to 2>><<endif>><<if $jammer is 1>>The robots have completed modifying the communications equipment to emit a jamming signal. \u000a\u000a<<set $jammer to 2>><<set $doom_xenocide += 5>><<endif>><<if $bio_lab is 1>>The robots have completed the bio lab.\u000a\u000a<<set $bio_lab to 2>><<endif>><<if $boat is 1>>Your boat is finished and sitting by the door. You fold it up and carry it on your back without issue.\u000a\u000a<<set $boat to 2>><<endif>><<if $stasis_net is 1>>Your stasis net is finished and sitting by the door. Looks sturdy enough to hold a small beast without issue.\u000a\u000a<<set $stasis_net to 2>><<endif>><<if $flight_suit is 1>>Your flight suit is ready and sitting by the door. You put it on and test it out. You feel ready to climb.\u000a\u000a<<set $flight_suit to 2>><<endif>><<if $bomb is 1>>Lucy's bomb is waiting for you by the door. You feel uncomfortable picking it up and carrying it around.\u000a\u000a<<set $bomb to 2>><<endif>><<if $refinery is 1>>The robots have completed building the refinery additions to the industrial area. They also took the liberty of starting the refining process on the ores you found. Several of them were processable into usable fuel.\u000a\u000a<<set $refinery to 2>><<set $fuel += 2>><<endif>><<if $ftl_fuel is 1>>Soto mentions to you that the isotopes are finished refining. There should be enough FTL fuel to send the Heroism anywhere it wants to go.\u000a\u000a<<set $ftl_fuel to 2>><<endif>><<if $cure and $cure < 4>><<set $cure += 1>><<$if cure is 4>>Inez has finished with the potential cure for the disease.<<else>>Inez continues to make progress searching for a cure for the disease afflicting the colony.<<endif>>\u000a\u000a<<endif>><<if $genome is 1>>Inez has finished analyzing the curious plant. It looks like it's engineered to be a database of various DNAs. How it has human DNA is a mystery. She should be able to change what DNAs are held on the plant.\u000a\u000a<<set $genome to 2>><<endif>><<if $hybrid_genome is 1>>Inez has finished splicing the crew's DNA into the plant. If theory is correct, inserting the plant into the antenna on the south island should "register" everyone as native, and end the aggressive behavior of the creatures around the colony.\u000a\u000a<<set $hybrid_genome to 2>><<endif>><<if $fuel is 0 and $aux_gen is 0>>The colony is rationing power already. Soto is already gone, arranging the solar mirrors in a desprate attempt to restore power to the colony.\u000a\u000a<<set $generator to 0>><<set $aux_gen to 2>><<endif>><<if $plasma_torch>>Your plasma torch burned off the excess charge in the night.\u000a\u000a<<set $plasma_torch to 0>><<endif>>\u000a\u000a[[Head out.|Colony Center]]
